quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,11,"Allah originates the creation, then He will bring it back, then you will be brought back to Him"
  30,12,"And when the Hour sets in, the guilty will despair"
  30,13,"None of those whom they ascribed as partners [to Allah] will intercede for them, and they will disavow their partners"
  30,14,"The day the Hour sets in, they will be divided on that day [in separate groups]"
  30,15,"As for those who have faith and do righteous deeds, they shall be in a garden, rejoicing"
  30,16,"But as for those who were faithless and denied Our signs and the encounter of the Hereafter, they will be brought to the punishment"
  30,17,So glorify Allah when you enter evening and when you rise at dawn
  30,18,"To Him belongs all praise in the heavens and the earth, at nightfall and when you enter noontime"
  30,19,"He brings forth the living from the dead, and brings forth the dead from the living, and revives the earth after its death. Likewise, you [too] shall be raised [from the dead]"